  <entry>
    <title>verilog_00</title>
    <link href="/2026/04/22/verilog-00/"/>
    <url>/2026/04/22/verilog-00/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>本实验实验Xilinks的xc7a75t系列FPGA</p><h3 id="一、ROM-IP-配置"><a href="#一、ROM-IP-配置" class="headerlink" title="一、ROM IP 配置"></a>一、ROM IP 配置</h3><p>ROM功能的实现可以采用分布式内存（Distributed Memory）或者块内存（BlockMemory）</p><table><thead><tr><th align="left">对比项</th><th align="left">分布式内存 (Distributed Memory)</th><th align="left">块内存 (Block Memory &#x2F; BRAM)</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="left">物理底座</td><td align="left">使用逻辑电路中的 LUT（查找表）</td><td align="left">FPGA 芯片中自带的专用存储块（Silicon Blocks）</td></tr><tr><td align="left">适合场景</td><td align="left">极小容量（如本示例的 16 depth）</td><td align="left">大容量、高带宽</td></tr><tr><td align="left">资源消耗</td><td align="left">消耗逻辑资源（LUTs），用多了会挤压逻辑空间</td><td align="left">消耗芯片上固定的 BRAM 块（不占用逻辑空间）</td></tr><tr><td align="left">灵活性</td><td align="left">非常快，配置灵活</td><td align="left">有固定格式，需按块使用</td></tr></tbody></table><p>本实验数据量极小（只需要深度只有16位），故采用分布式内存。</p><h4 id="双击IP-Catalog-搜索框输入：Distributed-Memory-Generator-并双击"><a href="#双击IP-Catalog-搜索框输入：Distributed-Memory-Generator-并双击" class="headerlink" title="双击IP Catalog,  搜索框输入：Distributed Memory Generator 并双击"></a>双击IP Catalog,  搜索框输入：Distributed Memory Generator 并双击</h4><h4 id="配置-memory-config-标签页"><a href="#配置-memory-config-标签页" class="headerlink" title="配置 memory config 标签页"></a>配置 memory config 标签页</h4><p>Depth 设置为16，实际只需要12种状态<br>Data Width 设置为11 ，4位位选加7位段选</p><h4 id="Port-config：保持默认"><a href="#Port-config：保持默认" class="headerlink" title="Port config：保持默认"></a>Port config：保持默认</h4><h4 id="配置-RST-Initialization-标签页"><a href="#配置-RST-Initialization-标签页" class="headerlink" title="配置 RST&amp;Initialization 标签页"></a>配置 RST&amp;Initialization 标签页</h4><p>Load COE File 中上传编辑好的coe文件<br>COE 文件（Coefficient File）是 Vivado 中专门用来初始化存储器内容的文件</p><p>COE Options<br>Default Data 默认数值填0；Radix 填16 进制</p><p>COE:</p><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c">memory_initialization_radix=<span class="hljs-number">16</span>;<br>memory_initialization_vector=<br><span class="hljs-number">01</span>E,<br><span class="hljs-number">01</span>D,<br><span class="hljs-number">01B</span>,<br><span class="hljs-number">017</span>,<br><span class="hljs-number">027</span>,<br><span class="hljs-number">047</span>,<br><span class="hljs-number">087</span>,<br><span class="hljs-number">08B</span>,<br><span class="hljs-number">08</span>D,<br><span class="hljs-number">08</span>E,<br><span class="hljs-number">10</span>E,<br><span class="hljs-number">20</span>E,<br><span class="hljs-number">000</span>,<br><span class="hljs-number">000</span>,<br><span class="hljs-number">000</span>,<br><span class="hljs-number">000</span>;<br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>OK、Generate并勾选global选项</p><h3 id="二、Verilog代码注意点"><a href="#二、Verilog代码注意点" class="headerlink" title="二、Verilog代码注意点"></a>二、Verilog代码注意点</h3><figure class="highlight c"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br><span class="line">13</span><br><span class="line">14</span><br><span class="line">15</span><br><span class="line">16</span><br><span class="line">17</span><br><span class="line">18</span><br><span class="line">19</span><br><span class="line">20</span><br><span class="line">21</span><br><span class="line">22</span><br><span class="line">23</span><br><span class="line">24</span><br><span class="line">25</span><br><span class="line">26</span><br><span class="line">27</span><br><span class="line">28</span><br><span class="line">29</span><br><span class="line">30</span><br><span class="line">31</span><br><span class="line">32</span><br><span class="line">33</span><br><span class="line">34</span><br><span class="line">35</span><br><span class="line">36</span><br><span class="line">37</span><br><span class="line">38</span><br><span class="line">39</span><br><span class="line">40</span><br><span class="line">41</span><br><span class="line">42</span><br><span class="line">43</span><br><span class="line">44</span><br><span class="line">45</span><br><span class="line">46</span><br><span class="line">47</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs c">module <span class="hljs-title function_">LED_SHOW</span><span class="hljs-params">(</span><br><span class="hljs-params">    input clk_3Hz,</span><br><span class="hljs-params">    input rst,</span><br><span class="hljs-params">    input en,    <span class="hljs-comment">//rst和en高电平有效</span></span><br><span class="hljs-params">    output reg [<span class="hljs-number">6</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] seg, </span><br><span class="hljs-params">    output reg [<span class="hljs-number">3</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] dig  </span><br><span class="hljs-params">)</span>;<br><br><br>reg [<span class="hljs-number">3</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0</span>]count;<br><br><span class="hljs-comment">//状态转换和动态显示的频率可以不同，但必须使用板上同一个时钟，切勿直接分频</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//尽量把所有逻辑都放在同一个时钟域下运行，避免亚稳态的出现</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//如果需要分频，可以引入使能位，结合原时钟域实现分频效果</span><br><span class="hljs-comment">//这里状态转换和动态显示直接使用同一个频率</span><br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">//12中状态切换</span><br>always @(posedge clk_50M or posedge rst) begin<br>    <span class="hljs-title function_">if</span> <span class="hljs-params">(rst)</span> <br>        count &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">4&#x27;b</span>0000;<br>    <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span>(en) begin <br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">if</span> (count == <span class="hljs-number">4&#x27;b</span>1011) count &lt;= <span class="hljs-number">0</span>;<br>        <span class="hljs-keyword">else</span> count &lt;= count + <span class="hljs-number">1</span>;<br>    end<br>end<br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">//ROM数据接收</span><br><br>wire [<span class="hljs-number">10</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0</span>] rom_data;<br><br>blk_mem_gen_1 <span class="hljs-title function_">rom_inst</span> <span class="hljs-params">(</span><br><span class="hljs-params">  .clka(clk_3Hz),</span><br><span class="hljs-params">  .addra(count),</span><br><span class="hljs-params">  .douta(rom_data)</span><br><span class="hljs-params">)</span>;<br><br><br><span class="hljs-comment">//动态显示</span><br>always @(posedge clk_3Hz) begin<br>    seg &lt;= rom_data[<span class="hljs-number">10</span>:<span class="hljs-number">4</span>];<br>    dig &lt;= rom_data[<span class="hljs-number">3</span>:<span class="hljs-number">0</span>];<br>end<br><br>endmodule<br><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
